FC Barcelona took a giant step towards winning the La Liga title after they beat Athletic Bilbao 2-0 on Sunday and nearest challengers Atletico Madrid lost 2-1 at Villarreal. The results gave the Catalans an 11-point lead at the top of the standings. Paco Alcacer took the place of suspended striker Luis Suarez in the starting line-up and scored a first goal in three months. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from The NEWS. Click here to read the full text on the original website.